channel.title: Project runescape
channel.description:
[size=20pt]PROJECT RUNESCAPE[/size] A.K.A a copy of non members world
I now started a new project after having a succesfull project (terrorwars v2) unreleased.
This project will be a copy of non member world,only difference is in :
some of the skills will not be as detailed some stuff will be different some things will be better Exp will be mush higher
-Now i know your thinking not another guy thats gone try this and fail but the truth is i,m already halfway i have all the methods and experience its just a matter of time completing it.
-Now i,m posting this as i need a litle favor. i want u to tell me what u want to be exported from members world to non members world.
WILL BE DONE : -Achievement dairy (for non member towns) -All Normal Magics (wave spells)
PENDING : -Duel Arena -Pickpocketing
SUGGESTED : -Duel Arena - -Pickpocketing - -Rest of Normal Magic ! -Ancient Magic x -God Spells x
NOT ALLOWED : -Any Member Item or Monster (why not ? brings far to many bugs whit it) -Any area from Member worlds (gates are closed and there staying that way) -God spells (Requires a god staff wich is a member item) -Ancient Magic (Requires a ancient staff wich is a member item)
